        Creates a new renamed result set metadata that renames the table name as the given new table name and the columns identified by the specified indices as the given names.
        Parameters:
        metaData - the result set metadata to be renamed.
        newTableName - the name name of the table in the renamed result set metadata.
        columns - the indices of the columns which will be renamed in the renamed result set metadata.
        newNames - the new names of the specified columns in the renamed result set metadata.
